    <div class="faq-a" id="failure-mode-4-intent-drift"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>We hit this with integration combo pages. The template targeted keyword pattern "[Tool A] integration with [Tool B]" but searchers were often looking for a comparison or a how-to, not an integration page.</p></div></div>
