    <div class="faq-a" id="failure-mode-5-stale-data-decay"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>We watched for this carefully. The dataset behind each template included data sources that had refresh frequencies. Glossary data refreshed annually. City data refreshed every 6 months. Integration combo data refreshed quarterly.</p></div></div>
