    <div class="faq-a" id="failure-mode-6-no-conversion-path"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Each template family had a CTA tied to the page topic. Glossary pages had a CTA to a related blog post or product feature page. City pages had a CTA to a region-specific demo request. Integration combo pages had a CTA to a free trial.</p></div></div>
