    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="why-this-math-beats-traditional-content"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A traditional blog post in the same niche cost the client $250 to $400 per article when produced internally. The team published 4 to 6 traditional articles per month, producing 72 to 108 articles in the same 18-month window.</p></div></div>
