    <div class="faq-a" id="can-you-do-programmatic-seo-with-ai-in-2026"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, but the system around the AI matters more than the AI itself. We use AI for drafting, brief expansion, and SEO formatting. Every page touches AI. None ship without human editing, fact-checking, and quality review. Pure AI-generated pages with no editorial layer perform 34% worse in rankings according to industry data. AI-assisted pages with proper governance perform 12% better than fully human-written content, per <a href="https://www.searchenginejournal.com/scaling-ai-content-is-the-1-enterprise-priority-how-do-you-scale-without-penalty/574518/">Search Engine Journal's enterprise scaling analysis</a>. The discipline is in the workflow, not the model.</p></div></div>
